# Dark Room Gallery App
A NodeJS web application that allows users to upload photos to the cloud, and display them on the browser. This project tests DevOps skills in Jenkins to deploy code using a pipeline. Notifications are sent to Slack and Email to the team when builds are successful or failed.

## Demo
The app has been published on Heroku(https://dry-springs-42834.herokuapp.com/)

## Installation
* Fork and Clone this repo https://github.com/kitmikai/gallery in this folder
* cd gallery
* Create a MongoDB cloud account at Mlab(https://mlab.com) on Atlas
* Create a collection in Atlas
* Create a Heroku account and install the CLI tools
* Set up Jenkins
* Create a pipeline in Jenkins
* Work on the project

## Built with
* HTML5
* NodeJS 
* CSS

